{
  "video_id": "mxNpNuogqsY",
  "title": "How my son's short life made a lasting difference | Sarah Gray",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13798.0,
      "end_time": 16271.0,
      "text": "I was three months pregnant with twins"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16295.000000000002,
      "end_time": 19639.0,
      "text": "when my husband Ross and I went to my second sonogram."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21221.0,
      "end_time": 23539.0,
      "text": "I was 35 years old at the time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23563.0,
      "end_time": 26883.0,
      "text": "and I knew that that meant we had a higher risk"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26907.0,
      "end_time": 28851.0,
      "text": "of having a child with a birth defect."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29907.0,
      "end_time": 32965.0,
      "text": "So, Ross and I researched the standard birth defects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 32989.0,
      "end_time": 34989.0,
      "text": "and we felt reasonably prepared."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 35973.0,
      "end_time": 37918.0,
      "text": "Well, nothing would have prepared us"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 37942.0,
      "end_time": 40996.0,
      "text": "for the bizarre diagnosis that we were about to face."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 42291.0,
      "end_time": 45830.0,
      "text": "The doctor explained that one of our twins, Thomas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 45854.0,
      "end_time": 48678.0,
      "text": "had a fatal birth defect called anencephaly."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 49476.0,
      "end_time": 52870.0,
      "text": "This means that his brain was not formed correctly"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 52894.0,
      "end_time": 54870.0,
      "text": "because part of his skull was missing."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 55663.0,
      "end_time": 59187.0,
      "text": "Babies with this diagnosis typically die in utero"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 59211.0,
      "end_time": 62782.0,
      "text": "or within a few minutes, hours or days of being born."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 65129.99999999999,
      "end_time": 68228.0,
      "text": "But the other twin, Callum,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 68252.0,
      "end_time": 72140.0,
      "text": "appeared to be healthy, as far as the doctor could tell,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 72164.0,
      "end_time": 76331.0,
      "text": "and these twins were identical,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 76355.0,
      "end_time": 77624.0,
      "text": "genetically identical."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 80125.0,
      "end_time": 84737.0,
      "text": "So after a lot of questions about how this could have possibly happened,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 84761.0,
      "end_time": 87896.0,
      "text": "a selective reduction was mentioned,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 87921.0,
      "end_time": 90822.0,
      "text": "and while this procedure was not impossible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 90846.0,
      "end_time": 95204.0,
      "text": "it posed some unique risks for the healthy twin and for me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 95228.0,
      "end_time": 97585.0,
      "text": "so we decided to carry the pregnancy to term."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 99101.0,
      "end_time": 103292.0,
      "text": "So there I was, three months pregnant, with two trimesters ahead of me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 103316.0,
      "end_time": 108195.0,
      "text": "and I had to find a way to manage my blood pressure and my stress."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 109268.0,
      "end_time": 114204.0,
      "text": "And it felt like having a roommate point a loaded gun at you for six months."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 115553.0,
      "end_time": 120483.0,
      "text": "But I stared down the barrel of that gun for so long"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 120507.0,
      "end_time": 122570.0,
      "text": "that I saw a light at the end of the tunnel."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 123506.0,
      "end_time": 126610.0,
      "text": "While there was nothing we could do to prevent the tragedy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 126634.0,
      "end_time": 129970.0,
      "text": "I wanted to find a way for Thomas&#39;s brief life"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 129121.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131342.0,
      "text": "to have some kind of positive impact."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 131366.0,
      "end_time": 135320.0,
      "text": "So I asked my nurse about organ, eye and tissue donation."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 136800.0,
      "end_time": 139601.0,
      "text": "She connected with our local organ-procurement organization,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 139625.0,
      "end_time": 141918.0,
      "text": "the Washington Regional Transplant Community."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 143359.0,
      "end_time": 145930.0,
      "text": "WRTC explained to me"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 145954.0,
      "end_time": 150355.0,
      "text": "that Thomas would probably be too small at birth to donate for transplant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 150379.0,
      "end_time": 151529.0,
      "text": "and I was shocked:"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 151553.0,
      "end_time": 153957.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t even know you could be rejected for that."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 153981.0,
      "end_time": 157393.0,
      "text": "But they said that he would be a good candidate to donate for research."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 158290.0,
      "end_time": 160321.0,
      "text": "This helped me see Thomas in a new light."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 160345.0,
      "end_time": 163240.0,
      "text": "As opposed to just a victim of a disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 163264.0,
      "end_time": 166851.0,
      "text": "I started to see him as a possible key to unlock a medical mystery."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 168288.0,
      "end_time": 171566.0,
      "text": "On March 23, 2010,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 171590.0,
      "end_time": 174970.0,
      "text": "the twins were born, and they were both born alive."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 175978.0,
      "end_time": 177644.0,
      "text": "And just like the doctor said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 177668.0,
      "end_time": 180747.0,
      "text": "Thomas was missing the top part of his skull,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 180771.0,
      "end_time": 182293.0,
      "text": "but he could nurse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 182318.0,
      "end_time": 183770.0,
      "text": "drink from a bottle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 183794.0,
      "end_time": 187930.0,
      "text": "cuddle and grab our fingers like a normal baby,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 187117.0,
      "end_time": 188714.0,
      "text": "and he slept in our arms."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 190530.0,
      "end_time": 193442.0,
      "text": "After six days, Thomas died in Ross&#39;s arms"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 193466.0,
      "end_time": 194862.0,
      "text": "surrounded by our family."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 196846.0,
      "end_time": 200981.0,
      "text": "We called WRTC, who sent a van to our home"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 201500.0,
      "end_time": 203543.0,
      "text": "and brought him to Children&#39;s National Medical Center."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 204751.0,
      "end_time": 208572.0,
      "text": "A few hours later, we got a call to say that the recovery was a success,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 208596.0,
      "end_time": 211830.0,
      "text": "and Thomas&#39;s donations would be going to four different places."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 212159.0,
      "end_time": 214554.0,
      "text": "His cord blood would go to Duke University."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 215208.0,
      "end_time": 219222.0,
      "text": "His liver would go to a cell-therapy company called Cytonet in Durham."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 220263.0,
      "end_time": 223508.0,
      "text": "His corneas would go to Schepens Eye Research Institute,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 223532.0,
      "end_time": 225691.0,
      "text": "which is part of Harvard Medical School,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 225715.0,
      "end_time": 228571.0,
      "text": "and his retinas would go to the University of Pennsylvania."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 230830.0,
      "end_time": 234110.0,
      "text": "A few days later, we had a funeral with our immediate family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 234350.0,
      "end_time": 235978.0,
      "text": "including baby Callum,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 236300.0,
      "end_time": 239316.0,
      "text": "and we basically closed this chapter in our lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 239718.0,
      "end_time": 242634.0,
      "text": "But I did find myself wondering, what&#39;s happening now?"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 243550.0,
      "end_time": 244722.0,
      "text": "What are the researchers learning?"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 245130.0,
      "end_time": 247423.0,
      "text": "And was it even worthwhile to donate?"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 249190.0,
      "end_time": 252741.0,
      "text": "WRTC invited Ross and I to a grief retreat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 252765.0,
      "end_time": 255517.0,
      "text": "and we met about 15 other grieving families"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 255542.0,
      "end_time": 258168.0,
      "text": "who had donated their loved one&#39;s organs for transplant."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 259494.00000000003,
      "end_time": 261895.00000000003,
      "text": "Some of them had even received letters"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 261918.0,
      "end_time": 264888.0,
      "text": "from the people who received their loved one&#39;s organs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 264912.0,
      "end_time": 266770.0,
      "text": "saying thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 267380.0,
      "end_time": 269227.0,
      "text": "I learned that they could even meet each other"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 269251.0,
      "end_time": 270688.0,
      "text": "if they&#39;d both sign a waiver,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 270713.0,
      "end_time": 272109.0,
      "text": "almost like an open adoption."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 272907.0,
      "end_time": 275746.0,
      "text": "And I was so excited, I thought maybe I could write a letter"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 275770.0,
      "end_time": 278378.0,
      "text": "or I could get a letter and learn about what happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 278403.0,
      "end_time": 279942.0,
      "text": "But I was disappointed to learn"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 279966.0,
      "end_time": 283136.0,
      "text": "that this process only exists for people who donate for transplant."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 283160.0,
      "end_time": 286422.0,
      "text": "So I was jealous. I had transplant envy, I guess."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 286446.0,
      "end_time": 287596.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 288104.0,
      "end_time": 290000.0,
      "text": "But over the years that followed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 290240.0,
      "end_time": 292500.0,
      "text": "I learned a lot more about donation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 292524.0,
      "end_time": 294602.0,
      "text": "and I even got a job in the field."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 294626.0,
      "end_time": 296390.0,
      "text": "And I came up with an idea."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 297879.0,
      "end_time": 299538.0,
      "text": "I wrote a letter that started out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 299562.0,
      "end_time": 300728.0,
      "text": "\"Dear Researcher.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 302468.0,
      "end_time": 304318.0,
      "text": "I explained who I was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 304342.0,
      "end_time": 308210.0,
      "text": "and I asked if they could tell me why they requested infant retinas"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 308234.0,
      "end_time": 310469.0,
      "text": "in March of 2010,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 310493.0,
      "end_time": 312762.0,
      "text": "and I asked if my family could visit their lab."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 313953.0,
      "end_time": 317490.0,
      "text": "I emailed it to the eye bank that arranged the donation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 317730.0,
      "end_time": 319450.0,
      "text": "the Old Dominion Eye Foundation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 319475.0,
      "end_time": 321967.0,
      "text": "and asked if they could send it to the right person."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 322395.0,
      "end_time": 324626.0,
      "text": "They said that they had never done this before,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 324650.0,
      "end_time": 326539.0,
      "text": "and they couldn&#39;t guarantee a response,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 326563.0,
      "end_time": 329378.0,
      "text": "but they wouldn&#39;t be an obstacle, and they would deliver it."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 330506.0,
      "end_time": 332696.0,
      "text": "Two days later, I got a response"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 332721.0,
      "end_time": 335705.0,
      "text": "from Dr. Arupa Ganguly of the University of Pennsylvania."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 336617.0,
      "end_time": 338239.0,
      "text": "She thanked me for the donation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 338263.0,
      "end_time": 340986.0,
      "text": "and she explained that she is studying retinoblastoma,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 341100.0,
      "end_time": 342827.0,
      "text": "which is a deadly cancer of the retina"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 342851.0,
      "end_time": 344977.0,
      "text": "that affects children under the age of five,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 345100.0,
      "end_time": 347691.0,
      "text": "and she said that yes, we were invited to visit her lab."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 348612.0,
      "end_time": 350254.0,
      "text": "So next we talked on the phone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 350278.0,
      "end_time": 352325.0,
      "text": "and one of the first things she said to me"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 352349.0,
      "end_time": 355180.0,
      "text": "was that she couldn&#39;t possibly imagine how we felt,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 355204.0,
      "end_time": 357944.0,
      "text": "and that Thomas had given the ultimate sacrifice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 357968.0,
      "end_time": 360550.0,
      "text": "and that she seemed to feel indebted to us."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 360709.0,
      "end_time": 363835.0,
      "text": "So I said, \"Nothing against your study,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 363859.0,
      "end_time": 365525.0,
      "text": "but we didn&#39;t actually pick it."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 365549.0,
      "end_time": 368707.0,
      "text": "We donated to the system, and the system chose your study."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 369493.0,
      "end_time": 374383.0,
      "text": "I said, \"And second of all, bad things happen to children every day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 374407.0,
      "end_time": 376195.0,
      "text": "and if you didn&#39;t want these retinas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 376219.0,
      "end_time": 378748.0,
      "text": "they would probably be buried in the ground right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 378773.0,
      "end_time": 382139.0,
      "text": "So to be able to participate in your study"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 382163.0,
      "end_time": 385806.0,
      "text": "gives Thomas&#39;s life a new layer of meaning."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 385830.0,
      "end_time": 388774.0,
      "text": "So, never feel guilty about using this tissue.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 389845.0,
      "end_time": 392379.0,
      "text": "Next, she explained to me how rare it was."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 392403.0,
      "end_time": 396990.0,
      "text": "She had placed a request for this tissue six years earlier"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 396123.0,
      "end_time": 398336.0,
      "text": "with the National Disease Research Interchange."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 399160.0,
      "end_time": 402494.0,
      "text": "She got only one sample of tissue that fit her criteria,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 402518.0,
      "end_time": 403722.0,
      "text": "and it was Thomas&#39;s."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 404958.0,
      "end_time": 408688.0,
      "text": "Next, we arranged a date for me to come visit the lab,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 408712.0,
      "end_time": 413361.0,
      "text": "and we chose March 23, 2015, which was the twins&#39; fifth birthday."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 414563.0,
      "end_time": 418498.0,
      "text": "After we hung up, I emailed her some pictures of Thomas and Callum,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 418523.0,
      "end_time": 421412.0,
      "text": "and a few weeks later, we received this T-shirt in the mail."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 423142.0,
      "end_time": 425941.0,
      "text": "A few months later, Ross, Callum and I piled in the car"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 425965.0,
      "end_time": 427556.0,
      "text": "and we went for a road trip."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 427580.0,
      "end_time": 430144.0,
      "text": "We met Arupa and her staff,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 430168.0,
      "end_time": 434416.0,
      "text": "and Arupa said that when I told her not to feel guilty, that it was a relief,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 434440.0,
      "end_time": 436741.0,
      "text": "and that she hadn&#39;t seen it from our perspective."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 438900.0,
      "end_time": 442328.0,
      "text": "She also explained that Thomas had a secret code name."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 442931.0,
      "end_time": 446300.0,
      "text": "The same way Henrietta Lacks is called HeLa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 446324.0,
      "end_time": 448950.0,
      "text": "Thomas was called RES 360."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 449394.0,
      "end_time": 450792.0,
      "text": "RES means research,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 450816.0,
      "end_time": 454316.0,
      "text": "and 360 means he was the 360th specimen"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 454340.0,
      "end_time": 456125.0,
      "text": "over the course of about 10 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 457133.0,
      "end_time": 461275.0,
      "text": "She also shared with us a unique document,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 461300.0,
      "end_time": 463785.0,
      "text": "and it was the shipping label"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 463809.0,
      "end_time": 467293.0,
      "text": "that sent his retinas from DC to Philadelphia."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 468273.0,
      "end_time": 471662.0,
      "text": "This shipping label is like an heirloom to us now."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 472304.0,
      "end_time": 475811.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the same way that a military medal or a wedding certificate might be."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 476687.0,
      "end_time": 482870.0,
      "text": "Arupa also explained that she is using Thomas&#39;s retina and his RNA"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 482111.0,
      "end_time": 485521.0,
      "text": "to try to inactivate the gene that causes tumor formation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 485545.0,
      "end_time": 488655.0,
      "text": "and she even showed us some results that were based on RES 360."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 489959.0,
      "end_time": 491793.0,
      "text": "Then she took us to the freezer"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 491817.0,
      "end_time": 495252.0,
      "text": "and she showed us the two samples that she still has"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 495276.0,
      "end_time": 497598.0,
      "text": "that are still labeled RES 360."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 497622.0,
      "end_time": 499482.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s two little ones left."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 499506.0,
      "end_time": 501340.0,
      "text": "She said she saved it"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 501580.0,
      "end_time": 503385.0,
      "text": "because she doesn&#39;t know when she might get more."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 504553.0,
      "end_time": 506601.0,
      "text": "After this, we went to the conference room"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 506625.0,
      "end_time": 509235.0,
      "text": "and we relaxed and we had lunch together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 509259.0,
      "end_time": 513529.0,
      "text": "and the lab staff presented Callum with a birthday gift."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 514179.0,
      "end_time": 515822.0,
      "text": "It was a child&#39;s lab kit."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 516419.0,
      "end_time": 518807.0,
      "text": "And they also offered him an internship."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 518831.0,
      "end_time": 522140.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 522380.0,
      "end_time": 525188.0,
      "text": "So in closing, I have two simple messages today."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 525578.0,
      "end_time": 529382.0,
      "text": "One is that most of us probably don&#39;t think about donating to research."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 529406.0,
      "end_time": 532516.0,
      "text": "I know I didn&#39;t. I think I&#39;m a normal person."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 532540.0,
      "end_time": 533690.0,
      "text": "But I did it."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 533715.0,
      "end_time": 535857.0,
      "text": "It was a good experience, and I recommend it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 535881.0,
      "end_time": 537824.0,
      "text": "and it brought my family a lot of peace."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 537849.0,
      "end_time": 540634.0,
      "text": "And second is if you work with human tissue"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 540658.0,
      "end_time": 543253.0,
      "text": "and you wonder about the donor and about the family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 543277.0,
      "end_time": 544472.0,
      "text": "write them a letter."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 544496.0,
      "end_time": 547312.0,
      "text": "Tell them you received it, tell them what you&#39;re working on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 547336.0,
      "end_time": 549300.0,
      "text": "and invite them to visit your lab,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 549270.0,
      "end_time": 551552.0,
      "text": "because that visit may be even more gratifying for you"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 551576.0,
      "end_time": 552807.0,
      "text": "than it is for them."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 552831.0,
      "end_time": 554593.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;d also like to ask you a favor."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 554617.0,
      "end_time": 557575.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;re ever successful in arranging one of these visits,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 557600.0,
      "end_time": 558918.0,
      "text": "please tell me about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 560640.0,
      "end_time": 561760.0,
      "text": "The other part of my family&#39;s story"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 561784.0,
      "end_time": 564960.0,
      "text": "is that we ended up visiting all four facilities"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 564120.0,
      "end_time": 566182.0,
      "text": "that received Thomas&#39;s donations."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 566206.0,
      "end_time": 569130.0,
      "text": "And we met amazing people doing inspiring work."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 570300.0,
      "end_time": 575104.0,
      "text": "The way I see it now is that Thomas got into Harvard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 575128.0,
      "end_time": 577294.0,
      "text": "Duke and Penn --"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 577318.0,
      "end_time": 580643.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 580667.0,
      "end_time": 583350.0,
      "text": "And he has a job at Cytonet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 583590.0,
      "end_time": 585843.0,
      "text": "and he has colleagues and he has coworkers"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 585868.0,
      "end_time": 587629.0,
      "text": "who are in the top of their fields."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 587653.0,
      "end_time": 590224.0,
      "text": "And they need him in order to do their job."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 591137.0,
      "end_time": 595787.0,
      "text": "And a life that once seemed brief and insignificant"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 595812.0,
      "end_time": 601494.0,
      "text": "revealed itself to be vital, everlasting and relevant."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 602224.0,
      "end_time": 604771.0,
      "text": "And I only hope that my life can be as relevant."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 605512.0,
      "end_time": 606662.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 606687.0,
      "end_time": 616415.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}